mal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eeaff97451b28926a404ebfb10c1a6b9b4ae119","tid":2042832,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T06:00:46.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7b78fc52eeaaf2df5f94c45fe9c5f7e22d5c6ff","tid":2042832,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T06:40:35.000Z","msg":"Pishhhhh"},{"pid":"072d5201f1b375dbfd82410a38c0f99b87617f48","tid":2042832,"uid":193026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T07:11:45.000Z","msg":"Sir, this way<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc24b0b6d7b39c244ddb0bc8cade29074e73edb7","tid":2042832,"uid":198175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T07:23:24.000Z","msg":"[而本地傳媒今早引述「金管局消息人士」指，聯緊匯率制度在1983年實施，比1992年更早，並不存在需要美國方面批准的問題。]<br />\n<br />\n又偷換概念, 講D唔講D<br />\n<br />\n1983年香港係英國殖民地, 美國認可英國在香港嘅統治權及港元的法定地位, 英美一直係盟友, 香港的英資銀行亦一直有在美國結算美元的權限, 當時使乜9立法容許港元轉美元?<br />\n<br />\n1997年後香港不再是英國殖民地, 中國沒有殖民地, 一個中國原則下只有人民幣, 咁美國先要另行立法訂明中共治下嘅香港特區享有特殊地位, 包括司法, 港元, 稅務, 貿易金融以至人民交流等.<br />\n<br />\n而家美國當香港真係中國不可分割嘅一部份, 玩到最盡可以連港元都不予承認, 點解仲要畀你用港元換美元?"},{"pid":"46136f200562d779b378a6fd9c922a5e909e480f","tid":2042832,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T07:24:08.000Z","msg":"[反國安法]&quot;反詩&quot;兩首<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2042910\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2042910</a>"},{"pid":"bdf79fee9dbcf3c487990b435d590abb10afd67d","tid":2042832,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T07:25:58.000Z","msg":"推核彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d576028e45c89e